## Limitations vs jj

| Aspect | jj | Our Approach |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Automatic | Every operation | Must opt-in or use wrapper |
| Storage | Content-addressed | Git stash (reflog-based) |
| Expiry | Managed by jj | Must manually clean up |
| Integration | Seamless | Explicit calls or wrappers |

